运营英语VTuber项目“IZUMO”的AnotherBall已累计筹集超过22亿日元https://p2y.jp/english-speaking-vtuber-project-izumo-operator-anotherball-raises-a-cumulative-total-of-about-over-2-2-billion-yen/ https://p2y.jp/english-speaking-vtuber-project-izumo-operator-anotherball-raises-a-cumulative-total-of-about-over-2-2-billion-yen/#respondp2y_admin Mon, 27 Nov 2023 05:49:05 +0000 VTuberバーチャルAnotherballIZUMOYouTuberバーチャルYouTuber資金調達 https://p2y.jp/?p=107410 <p> AnotherBall Co., Ltd. 为英语国家运营 VTuber 项目“IZUMO”，于 2023 年 11 月 27 日在种子轮融资中筹集了 19 亿日元，使融资总额达到约 22 […]</p> <a href="https://p2y.jp/english-speaking-vtuber-project-izumo-operator-anotherball-raises-a-cumulative-total-of-about-over-2-2-billion-yen/">运营英语 VTuber 项目“IZUMO”的 postAnotherBall 已筹集了总计超过 22 亿日元的资金首次</a>出现在<a href="https://p2y.jp">P2y.jp</a>上。; <p></p><p>面向英语国家运营 VTuber 项目“ <strong>IZUMO</strong> ”的<strong>AnotherBall Co., Ltd.</strong>于 2023 年 11 月 27 日在种子轮融资中筹集了 19 亿日元，使融资总额达到约 22 亿日元。它已经变得超级了。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1100" height="619" data-attachment-id="107416" data-permalink="https://p2y.jp/english-speaking-vtuber-project-izumo-operator-anotherball-raises-a-cumulative-total-of-about-over-2-2-billion-yen/english_speaking_vtuber_project_izumo_operator_anotherball_raises_a_cumulative_total_of_about_over_2_2_billion_yen/" data-orig-file="https://i0.wp.com/p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/english_speaking_vtuber_project_izumo_operator_anotherball_raises_a_cumulative_total_of_about_over_2_2_billion_yen.jpg?fit=1200%2C675&amp;ssl=1" data-orig-size="1200,675" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quo